node.text: Sunway Music Society 1st Official Welcome Session!

What's Up Musicians!!! 🎼

Sunway Music Society is back with the next Jamming Session 🎤 event! Interested in performing? Make sure to join right now and jam along our amazing houseband:

Vocals: @legitimnico 🎤
Bass: @tommoisclueless 🐟🎸
Guitar: @baodonk 🎸
Keys: @ethankw.leong 🎹
Drums: @azmilaq_ 🥁
Sax: @luqbrc 🎷

Date: 11/10/2023 
Time: 6pm to 10pm
Venue: JC2

We hope to see you there! 👋

Registration link in bio 
👉 @sunwaymusicsociety

✨ Share the Sunway Za Rocku Official Poster on your story (On Public Setting)
✨ Comment down below " It's time to Rock 🔥 (tag a friend) "
✨ Collect your free voucher at the Sunway Za Rocku
